post.description:
Booking request be send to webhook endpoint
     
    Triggers of the booking webhook:

       * POST /muntra-bookings/{id}/reschedule
       * POST /muntra-bookings
       * POST /muntra-booking-attendees/{id}/reschedule
       * POST /muntra-booking-attendees
       * POST /bookings/book
       * POST /bookings/rebook
       * POST /bookings with user_ids/patient_ids
       * PATCH /bookings
       * POST /booking-attendees for attendees with related user/patient
       * PATCH /booking-attendees for attendees with related user/patient
       * POST /bookings/{id}/cancel
       * POST /bookings/{id}/change
       * POST /rebookings/{id}/tentative-book
Journal entry request be send to webhook endpoint
Patient request be send to webhook endpoint
Task request be send to webhook endpoint
Verification request be send to webhook endpoint
